                                   ------------------------------------------------------------------

Headings               -- (from h1 to h6) h1 একটি পৃষ্ঠা একবার ব্যবহার করা যেতে পারে
Paragraphs             -- p
Style                  -- style="text-align: center; color: green; font-size:50px; background-color:black"
Formatting             -- <b>/<i>/<strong>/<small>/<mark>/<del>/<ins>/<sub>/<sup>
Quotation              -- <q>---</q>
Blockquote             --</blockquote>  দুই পাশে জায়গা ছেড়ে দেয়
Quotation & Citation   -- <q>/</blockquote>/<br>/<address>/<bdo dir=”rtl”>--</bdo>/    <abbr title=”--”>---<abbr>

                                           ------------------+--------------------

Links                     --  <a href="-"  target="_blank"></a>
Comments                  -- <!--comment-->
Color                     ---
                          --- https://flatuicolors.com/  https://htmlcolorcodes.com/  colorzilla >add       
                                Hex to rgb color converter >> https://www.rapidtables.com/convert/color/hex-to-rgb.html 

                                           --------------------+------------------

Images                    --- <img src="-" alt="-" width="42" height="42"   or style=”width:42;”>
Tables                    ---  
Lists                     ---1.Order 2.Unorder 3.Description  List  
                                 <ul style=”list-style-type: circle/square/none/disc ”>/<li> --------- <ol type=”a”>/<li>

                                          --------------------+--------------------

Block elements           ---<div>/<h>/<form>/<li>/<ol>/<ul>/<nav>/<p> 
                                    https://www.w3resource.com/html/HTML-block-level-and-inline-elements.php

Inline  elements         --- a, button, br, img, q, span, sub, sup,textarea    
                                   https://www.w3resource.com/html/HTML-block-level-and-inline-elements.php
       
